item.title: CVE-2014-4651|2024-08-06T11:20:27.020Z -- apache -- apache%20jclouds
item.description: It was found that the jclouds scriptbuilder Statements class wrote a temporary file to a predictable location. An attacker could use this flaw to access sensitive data, cause a denial of service, or perform other attacks.
